## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

### Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Padhysai/todox.git
cd todox

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .
```

